text: ZZzzzZZZzzzZZZZZzzzt "Hey bestie, can you hear me? Signal's a little weak. Contacting you this way so no one can eavesdrop on us. You were SO cool out there!" :^O "You made it look like a piece of cake."
"Thanks!"
"That mission was actually super difficult."
"Stop! You're gonna make me blush!"
"Don't mention it! You're doing all the work here after all. Sorry I can't be more helpful." :^(
"Acting as my handler is helpful!"
"Don't worry, just do what you can."
"You're useless!"
"It was?? Couldn't tell from my end. Don't worry, the next mission should really be a piece of cake."
"I hope so."
"What? Bring on the challenge! I live for it!"
"Hehe, what if I LIKE making you blush?" ;^)
"Don't get distracted! We gotta focus on the mission!"
"Well I suppose I can't stop you..." (˵◕‿◕˵)

"Is something wrong? I might have botched the connection." :^| "Looks like you can't reply, but you should be able to hear me. Just wanted to tell you how AMAZING you were out there. Stage 1 is complete, but stage 2 will be much, much more challenging. Expect another email from me soon!"
Goodbye!
"Alright alright, I'll try and hold off on the compliments until *after* we're out of here. Catch you later bestie, I'll have the next mission ready for you soon."
Goodbye!
"In that case you better prepare yourself!" ;;^)) "Keep looking cool out there and I'll shower you with praise! I gotta log off for now though, expect another email with your next assignment soon."
Goodbye!
"I hesitate to even call it a mission, more of a quick errand. I'll email you details soon."
Goodbye!
"Sorry bestie, your next mission will only be as difficult as you make it for yourself! I'm logging off now, email you again soon."
Goodbye!
"Thanks for appreciating me." :^) "Always wanted to be a handler, seems like I really fit the role huh? I'm gonna get back to work, your next assignment should appear in your inbox soon."
Goodbye!
"Will do! I'll have your next assignment ready soon, keep an eye on your inbox."
Goodbye!

"Not as useless as a dumb meathead like you." ;^) "I'm out here doing the REAL work while you're doing what? Completing missions? Pfff, as if that even compares." ;;^)) "You crack  me up bestie, I'll shoot the next assignment to your inbox soon."
Goodbye!
